'''''burzum''''' is a word in [[Black Speech]] which translates to "darkness". It is found within the [[Ring-inscription]]. It is formed from the stem ''[[búrz]]'' ("dark") and the particularizing suffix or 'article' ''um''.<ref>{{PE|Eldarin}}, pp. 11-12</ref>{{references}}
